	PRINTFORMLC <14> %SAVESTR:表記／膣% Term
	PRINTFORML ：%VAGINA_CALL_ENG(CSTR:性器呼び方／膣)%／%VAGINA_CALL_ENG(CSTR:性器呼び方／膣／蕩け)%
	PRINTFORMLC <15> %SAVESTR:表記／アナル% Term
	PRINTFORML ：%ANUS_CALL_ENG(CSTR:性器呼び方／アナル)%／%ANUS_CALL_ENG(CSTR:性器呼び方／アナル／蕩け)%
